## 런타임 시스템

### 1. 가비지 컬렉션 통합

```rust
pub struct GarbageCollector {
    heap: HashMap<u64, HeapObject>,
    marked: HashSet<u64>,
}

impl GarbageCollector {
    pub fn mark_and_sweep(&mut self, roots: &[StackFrame]) {
        // Phase 1: Mark reachable objects
        for root in roots {
            self.mark_recursive(root);
        }

        // Phase 2: Sweep unreachable objects
        let mut to_remove = Vec::new();
        for (id, obj) in &self.heap {
            if !self.marked.contains(id) {
                to_remove.push(*id);
            }
        }
        for id in to_remove {
            self.heap.remove(&id);
        }
        self.marked.clear();
    }
}
```

### 2. Foreign Function Interface (FFI)

```rust
pub struct FFIEngine {
    loaded_libs: HashMap<String, *mut libc::c_void>,
    bindings: HashMap<String, ExternalLink>,
}

impl FFIEngine {
    pub fn call_external(&self, symbol: &str, args: Vec<Value>) -> Result<Value> {
        // 1. 심볼 조회
        let link = self.bindings.get(symbol)?;

        // 2. 타입 검증
        if args.len() != link.arg_types.len() {
            return Err("Argument count mismatch");
        }

        // 3. C 함수 호출
        unsafe {
            let func_ptr = dlsym(link.lib_name, link.symbol);
            // Call func_ptr with args...
        }
    }
}
```

### 3. 비동기 런타임

```rust
pub struct AsyncRuntime {
    executor: ThreadPool,
    futures: HashMap<u64, Box<dyn Future>>,
}

pub async fn async_call(f: Future<T>) -> T {
    self.executor.spawn(f).await
}
```

